The module package pyweblib consists of several submodules:
pyweblib.forms
    class library for handling <FORM> input
pyweblib.session
    server-side web session handling
pyweblib.helper
    misc. stuff useful in CGI-BINs
pyweblib.sslenv
    retrieves SSL-related env vars
pyweblib.httphelper
